  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      -  Randomized controlled trial comparing specialized AF Clinic with 'care as usual'

        -  Hypothesis: treatment of AF patients in the AF-Clinic by a nurse, specialised in AF,
           using guideline-based dedicated software, under supervision of a cardiologist, is
           efficient, safe and not inferior to care as usual by a cardiologists.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
